{
  "stem": "10406.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so he drew out his revolver, which to me looked like a cannon.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he cocked it, and put it to my forehead, and said, is anybody up there?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because if we find somebody up there, you're kaput.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I said, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he climbed up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One of them climbed up the steps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The other one was standing downstairs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he had a flashlight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Luckily, my aunts and my family were hiding in an-- in an attic which was like at the end of the main attic and was like boarded up a little-- closed off.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he looked and he looked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually, something-- there was a noise up there like something fell, which maybe scared him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and-- and then he decided that there was nothing there and came down.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then he asked me where-- where the garden was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had a big garden in the back of the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they-- they went out to the garden.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, going out to the garden, they were right underneath the part of the attic where everybody was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and-- and I was only hoping that somebody doesn't cough at that point.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Or some noise, or they don't look up and get suspicious, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in fact, one of them did look.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they walked out into the garden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they spent maybe five minutes or so, or 10, searching the garden because everything was grown high already.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like summer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I heard them coming back on the side of the house and like leaving-- leaving the area.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when I heard them, you know, pass the house and leave, and my teeth started chattering then like-- like a machine gun.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's when I started shaking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, I went back [? bed. ?]",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
